asset_contract.name: FLUF
asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)

description: Wainfluf was born with a cleft ear and the doctor told his parents that he should not be sent to school or taught until he was ten. He was raised on a strict diet of carrot soup.   As a youth, he was often truant from school and spent much of his childhood wandering around Flufland. He subsequently studied at the West Flufberry School of Art and was eventually a teacher there for a short period.  At the age of 20, he was left to support his mother and his 46 sisters after his father's death. Louis became famous for his whimsical bunny art, depicting Flufs doing perfectly normal Fluf things in an original and heartwarming style.  Wainfluf’s location is currently unknown, but many suspect he is driving into the next sunset

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle.

name: Cunni Esquilax
description: Cuniculo Esquilax immigrated from Spain with her parents when she was a baby.Her parents ran a convenience store, where she would help stacking shelves  serving customers.She was an average student at school but she was the star netballer for her high school team, where she played the centre position.She took up waitressing after leaving school but now works as a bar tender at the Tiki Bar.She loves watching DJ Myxxi Tryxx when she performs sets at the club.Dancing is one of her passions in life.Cunni has a crush on Bugattii Bunny, because he loves to flirt with her when he is at the bar  he makes her laugh.Cunni does not really know what she wants to do with her life so she just takes each day as it comes because she believes life is all about the journey  living in the moment.

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection.

Welcome to the Fluffle.
